{"tid":167310,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好攰。。。。。。。。。。","createTime":"2017-03-22T17:25:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-22T18:09:03.000Z","uid":23170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bd63de100e3a69a09acab2ef8270a483bd359076","tid":167310,"uid":23170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T17:25:37.000Z","msg":"好似對其他人做啲乜都唔啱咁。我人格果然係有問題，唔係點會成日都會淪落返咁嘅環境。越黎越覺得同人相處好煩，係咪我要求太多，太自私。。唔識得顧人感受。其實我都知問題喺邊。。應該係我仆街。咁都無得怪邊個。真係好攰。。。"},{"pid":"6ed67edd6e6d9943e5d658df1e2357ee34a96437","tid":167310,"uid":41737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T17:26:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"24b689c784c0a7af496281d7725625a5602629f4","tid":167310,"uid":30578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T17:27:00.000Z","msg":"行撚開"},{"pid":"779ef906884c9a1f53ab9519f704416dfb04eba1","tid":167310,"uid":21355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T17:27:03.000Z","msg":"我都唔想同人相處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2c7da5bd2db3756fda07c004d3e5f91f95c7d35","tid":167310,"uid":10759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T17:27:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c47b9ee90a75405d1d4b5c78841a0a744607962","tid":167310,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T17:31:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>攰就攬住我訓</blockquote><br />\n我都好想可以攬住任何一個人瞓。。返學都已經好多嘢諗。但係都係分唔到心，諗起好多唔同人嘅嘢就覺得自己好垃圾。。"},{"pid":"886924a21eb4d1131c3db524d34d507762b17230","tid":167310,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T17:34:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都唔想同人相處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我一直都好憎同人相處。特別係啲無謂人，見到佢地啲面口就憎，懶係好人嗰啲樣，真係寧願成世一個人都唔想見到。或者自己同我心入面嘅無謂人都係一樣，見高拜見低踩。但係成日好似真係識落左都係會因為自己痴左線將個人推返開。。真心覺得自己垃圾。係咪剩係值得成世孤獨。。。"},{"pid":"21a07f92a0719cd0f77c922ae01c17a62acd8b33","tid":167